dat <- data.frame(5) #read.csv('dat1.csv')
colnames(dat)<-'tf'

nsample<-nrow(dat)
data_list<-list(k=dat$tf, N=10, n=nrow(dat))

mcmc_result<-stan(
  file='dat1.stan',
  data=data_list,
  seed=1,
  chains=2,
  iter=20000,
  warmup=1000,
  thin=1
)
print(mcmc_result, probs=c(0.025,0.5,0.975))
